column5: it depends on how or why they are using my photo I had a lodge I had never been at use a photo of me with a big pike and a fish gif I used here  and they even had the nerve to just link to where I had it hosted......  I changed the photo and gif to a bunch of words describing a sex act and something about his mother too.. went back to the site and the old photo was still there refreshed the page and low and behold there were the words of wisdom..........I bet he never steals photos  or animations again
